description: This header file declares exported API functions for Authentication Message objects used in the BroadWay Service Delivery System. It defines prototypes for creating, removing, enrolling objects, and initializing both request and response message objects, serving as an interface for module interaction within the system.

methods.name: CfFRComponentCreate
methods.description: Creates a request message object for authentication filtering.

methods.name: CfFRCOCreate
methods.description: Creates a specific request message object for authentication filtering.

methods.name: CfFRCOEnrollObjects
methods.description: Enrolls necessary objects for the request message.

methods.name: CfFPComponentCreate
methods.description: Creates a response message object for authentication filtering.

methods.name: CfFPCOCreate
methods.description: Creates a specific response message object for authentication filtering.

methods.name: CfFPCOEnrollObjects
methods.description: Enrolls necessary objects for the response message.
